                    </div>
                    <span>Well written, short and to the point this book has served me well.  I bought it for what my classmates considered a minor presentation.  I learned no presentation has to be minor and impressed my classmates, professors and any other audience under any occasion or circumstance.  </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">The Fundamentals</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
