                    </div>
                    <span>Red Auerbach used to teach his legendary Boston Celtics to stick to the fundamentals. This book is filled with help to make your speeches memorable. This book will add impact to your next talk whether in school, work or a one on one meeting. The author presumes a basic knowledge of speech construction. If you want help with that read Jack Valenti.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">good, a bit conservative but good</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
